reviews.text: Great staff, great location, dart machines are in good working order and reasonably priced. The food is good, drinks are also good and consistent with Hong Kong pricing.

Best for dart in town.
Come to this rowdy hidden gem in Sheung Wan if you're looking to drink hard, play some beer pong or try your hand at the electric dart boards.
Nice place😊
